To rebuild this server:
1. Install docker
2. Install docker-compose
3. Install duckdns
4. Install firefox "gcp: also need to install xauth"
5. Install nginx-proxy-manager **
6. Install portainer
7. Install mariadb
8. Install nextcloud
9. Install watchtower

** Use firefox and x11 display forwarding to configure (very slow)
** "VcXsrv X Server" is needed for Windows 10

---

portainer           http://localhost:9000   docker exec -it duckdns /bin/bash
duckdns             ---                     docker exec -it duckdns /bin/bash
nginx-proxy-manager http://localhost:8181   docker exec -ti nginx-proxy-manager sh
nextcloud           https://localhost:4443  docker exec -it nextcloud /bin/bash

Start all docker containers:  docker start $(docker ps -a -q)
Stop all docker containers:  docker stop $(docker ps -q)
Restart all docker containers:  docker restart $(docker ps -q)

Copy from container to host:  docker cp -a nginx-proxy-manager:/config/letsencrypt ./
Copy from remote host to container:  scp -i ~/.ssh/my-ssh-key local-file-path username@ip-address:~

---

Microsoft Window Apps
- Putty
- vcxsvr
- WinSCP
